Tapping the button below will allow you to unlock the desired door fit with the Sense Lock system.
Tapping the button below will allow you to view various application logs such as when an account was created, when you used the Sense Lock app to unlock a door and much more.
Tapping the button below will allow you to write login credentials to an RFID card or tag. Note: This option cannot be used to erase information on a card. Please make sure you are certain about the card/tag you are writing to!
//From NDEF file
CardEmulation Sample Sample Loyalty Card Account Number
//From NDED file (Base-Strings)
This sample demonstrates how to emulate an NFC card, using the "host card emulation" feature added in Android 4.4. This sample makes the device appear as a loyalty card whenever the screen is on and the user taps their device on an appropriately configured NFC reader.
The "CardReader" sample can be used to read the loyalty card implemented in this sample.
/From NDED file (fragment-strings) Show Log Hide Log
